---
title: Charred Halloumi Wraps (v) with Sweet Potato Chips  and Yoghurty Carrot Salad
description: If you’re looking for a quick-fix comforting veggie recipe, look no further than our charred halloumi wraps. With just ten minutes hands-on cooking time, they really are as easy to assemble as they are to eat... Wrapped up in toasted whole-wheat tortillas and served with sweet potato wedges and a yoghurty carrot salad (the secret ingredient in the dressing is a game changer!), you can’t go wrong with this deliciously simple veggie recipe.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/charred-halloumi-wraps-64a07466-6378f869.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/charred-halloumi-wraps-5a9937ad30006c057a1ca8c2-e44a81de.pdf
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/charred-halloumi-wraps-5a9937ad30006c057a1ca8c2
author: Mimi Morley
time required: 35m
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 911 kcal
